Name: SBK Generations
Overview: Play through the last 4 seasons of the SBK world championships, including the new 2012 season to become world champion or test your skills in the new SBK Experience mode. With SBK Generations, Milestone has developed what they consider to be the definitive motorcycle game, filled with over 220+ riders, 60 bike models, 140+ teams, 17 circuits and up to 16 player online multi-player.
